status=[]
for j in df.index:
    if df['Status'][j] == 1:
        status.append(j)

for i in df.columns:
    col = df[i]
    tipaje = np.array(col)
    if len(col.unique()) == 1:
        print('La variable '+str(i)+' ha sido eliminada debido a que solo tiene un valor')
        df.drop(i,axis=1,inplace=True)
        
    if tipaje.dtype == 'float64' or tipaje.dtype == 'int64':
        if True in np.isnan(col.unique()):
            existencia = np.isnan(col[status])
            conteo = 0
            for n in status:
                if existencia[n]== True:
                    conteo += 1
            if conteo/(len(status)) >= .1:
                print('La variable '+str(i)+' ha sido eliminada contar con un ' + str(round((conteo/(len(status)))*100))+ ' % de datos faltantes en status 1')
                df.drop(i,axis=1,inplace=True)

columnas_no_numericas = df.select_dtypes(exclude=['number']).columns.tolist()
mapeos = {}
valores_originales = []
valores_numericos = []
columnas_no_numericas

for columna in columnas_no_numericas:
    valores_uniques = df[columna].unique()
    # mapeo de valores originales a valores numricos
    mapeo = {valor_original: valor_numerico for valor_numerico, valor_original in enumerate(valores_uniques)}
    mapeos[columna] = mapeo
    
    # Aplicar la conversin a valores numricos en el DataFrame original
    df[columna] = df[columna].map(mapeo)
    
    valores_originales.append(valores_uniques)
    valores_numericos.append(df[columna].unique())

#  DataFrame con los valores originales y numricos
valores_unicos = pd.DataFrame({'Columna': columnas_no_numericas,
                               'Original': valores_originales,
                               'Numerico': valores_numericos})
print(valores_unicos) #valoresparaelmapeo

def arbol(x,y,criterio,prof,poda):
    dt = DecisionTreeClassifier(class_weight=None, criterion=criterio,max_depth=prof,max_features=None,max_leaf_nodes=None,
                             min_samples_leaf=1,min_samples_split=2, min_weight_fraction_leaf=poda,random_state=None,
                             splitter='best')
    dt = dt.fit(x,y)
    x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x, y, test_size = 0.90, random_state = None)
    y_pred = dt.predict(x_test)
    r = metrics.accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred)
    print('Exactitud: ' , metrics.accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred))
    class_names = ['0','1']

    plt.figure()
    sns.heatmap(metrics.confusion_matrix(y_test,y_pred),annot=True,fmt='3.0f',
            xticklabels=('0','1'),yticklabels=('0','1'),
            cmap=sns.cubehelix_palette(as_cmap=True))
    plt.xlabel('Predicted Labels')
    plt.ylabel('True Labels')
    plt.title('Confusion matrix',y=1.06, size=15)
    
    r_probs = [0 for _ in range (len( y_test ) )]
    dt_probs = dt.predict_proba( x_test )
    dt_probs = dt_probs[:, 1]


    r_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, r_probs)
    dt_auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, dt_probs)

    r_fpr, r_tpr, _ = roc_curve(y_test, r_probs)
    dt_fpr, dt_tpr, _ = roc_curve(y_test, dt_probs)
    plt.figure()
    plt.plot(r_fpr, r_tpr, linestyle='--', label='Random prediction (AUROC = %0.3f)' % r_auc)
    plt.plot(dt_fpr, dt_tpr, marker='.', label='Decision Tree (AUROC = %0.3f)' % dt_auc)
    
    plt.title('ROC Plot')
    plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')
    plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')
    plt.legend()
    plt.show()
    
    print(metrics.f1_score(y_test,y_pred))
    
    y_pred_prob = dt.predict_proba(x_test)

    loss = log_loss(y_test, y_pred_prob)
    print("Prdida:", loss)

    # Calcular la curva de prdida
    train_sizes, train_losses, test_losses = learning_curve(dt, x, y, cv=5, scoring='neg_log_loss')

    # Convertir las puntuaciones de prdida a positivas
    train_losses = -train_losses
    test_losses = -test_losses

    # Calcular la media y la desviacin estndar de las puntuaciones de prdida
    train_losses_mean = np.mean(train_losses, axis=1)
    train_losses_std = np.std(train_losses, axis=1)
    test_losses_mean = np.mean(test_losses, axis=1)
    test_losses_std = np.std(test_losses, axis=1)

    # Graficar la curva de prdida
    plt.figure()
    plt.fill_between(train_sizes, train_losses_mean - train_losses_std, train_losses_mean + train_losses_std, alpha=0.1)
    plt.fill_between(train_sizes, test_losses_mean - test_losses_std, test_losses_mean + test_losses_std, alpha=0.1)
    plt.plot(train_sizes, train_losses_mean, 'o-', color="r", label="Prdida de entrenamiento")
    plt.plot(train_sizes, test_losses_mean, 'o-', color="g", label="Prdida de prueba")
    plt.xlabel('Tamao del conjunto de entrenamiento')
    plt.ylabel('Prdida')
    plt.title('Curva de Prdida')
    plt.legend(loc="best")
    plt.grid(True)
    plt.show()
    
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(70,40))
    tree.plot_tree(dt, fontsize=10,feature_names=list(x.columns.values))
